definition.value: A benzylisoquinoline alkaloid muscle relaxant which constitutes the active component of curare.
A member of the class of beta-carbolines that is tubulosan bearing methoxy groups at positions 10 and 11 and a hydroxy group at the 8' position.
A germacranolide based on a 2,3,3a,4,5,8,9,11a-octahydrocyclodeca[b]furan-4-yl skeleton.
